    <dashboard name='Story 1' type='storyboard'>
      <layout-options>
        <title>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000'>Indigo Airlines - Booking &amp; Revenue Analysis </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </title>
      </layout-options>
      <style>
        <style-rule element='story-description'>
          <format attr='font-family' value='Tableau Bold' />
          <format attr='font-size' value='11' />
          <format attr='color' value='#000000' />
        </style-rule>
        <style-rule element='story-point-caption'>
          <format attr='width' value='1157' />
          <format attr='font-size' value='16' />
          <format attr='font-weight' value='bold' />
          <format attr='font-family' value='Tableau Bold' />
          <format attr='background-color' value='#0055ff' />
        </style-rule>
      </style>
      <size maxheight='768' maxwidth='1366' minheight='768' minwidth='1366' preset-index='0' sizing-mode='fixed' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='2' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='97916' id='1' param='vert' removable='false' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98828' x='586' y='1042'>
            <zone h='4297' id='3' type-v2='title' w='98828' x='586' y='1042' />
            <zone fixed-size='109' h='14193' id='4' is-fixed='true' paired-zone-id='5' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard-nav' w='98828' x='586' y='5339' />
            <zone h='79426' id='5' paired-zone-id='4' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard' w='98828' x='586' y='19532'>
              <flipboard active-id='4' nav-type='caption' show-nav-arrows='true'>
                <story-points>
                  <story-point caption='&quot;Indigo Airlines processed 50,000 booking attempts - but only 14.9% were completed. This analysis investigates why, and identifies where revenue can be grown.&quot;' captured-sheet='KPI Sheet' id='1' />
                  <story-point caption='“Internet (Desktop) generates most revenue, while Mobile has low volume despite similar booking value. Mobile is a major growth opportunity.”' captured-sheet='Revenue by Sales Channel' id='2' />
                  <story-point caption='“Add-ons are the strongest revenue lever. Customers selecting 3 add-ons pay much more than customers selecting none.”' captured-sheet='Add-on impact' id='3' />
                  <story-point caption='“Three actions can improve revenue: fix completion rate, improve mobile conversion, and promote add-on bundles.”' captured-sheet='' id='4' />
                </story-points>
              </flipboard>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='71615' id='7' story-point-id='4' type-v2='text' w='83968' x='12958' y='21745'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontsize='24'> 1. Fix the Completion Rate</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontsize='24'>   ~ Only 14.9% of bookings complete. Investigate checkout </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontsize='24'>    drop-off and add abandoned-booking email reminders.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontsize='24'>    Even +5% improvement.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontsize='24'>  2. Launch Add-on Bundle Packages</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontsize='24'>   ~  3 add-ons , Create a Smart Traveller Bundle at a 10% discount </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontsize='24'>    to increase attachment from 0-add-on customers.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontsize='24'>3. Fix Mobile Conversion</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontsize='24'> ~  Mobile customers pay the same as Internet customers </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontsize='24'>    but complete far fewer bookings. Fix the mobile </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontsize='24'>    checkout flow to capture this lost revenue.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <simple-id uuid='{37F28D03-D38E-4901-B651-434749712249}' />
    </dashboard>
